net.sereneproject.collector.service
Interface AnalyzerService

All Known Implementing Classes:
AnalyzerServiceImpl
public interface AnalyzerService

Service used to dispatch probe values to analyzers. This service is responsible of locating the analyzers, preparing messages and handling results from the analyzers.
